      <p><strong>A. INFORMATION YOU CHOOSE TO PROVIDE</strong></p>
      <p>If you register using Facebook or Twitter, you are allowing us access to your Facebook or Twitter account. By allowing us to access your Facebook or Twitter account, you understand that we will obtain and may share certain of your information including your public profile, name, and profile picture. We only obtain information from your Facebook or Twitter account that you specifically authorize and grant us permission to obtain. If we ever add to the list of Facebook or Twitter authorizations you will be required to give your permission again.</p>
