      <p>Research: In addition to the uses outlined above, by using our Services you agree to allow us to anonymously utilize your usage information to research trends and promotion efficacy. This research is intended to improve the user experience and may be be published on our site, emails, blogs or promotional materials. All of your responses and specific experiences are kept anonymous.</p>

